name: Safe & Warm Hoodie PREORDER
description: Finally, our first pull-over hoodie. This design will be printed on a dark heather 50/50 hooded pull-over (ignore the background color). This is only a preorder item, so you must pre-pay and send all your information in order to get on. Repeat, this item is ONLY PREORDER. To get one, you must pre-pay and give all your information. We won't be selling them out, and if you order one you can pick it up at the NEWSHOES CHRISTMAS SHOW DECEMBER 21st, or we can send it to you. However, they won't be in until December. So that gives you plenty of time to get it together and order one of these. We promise, it will keep you "safe and warm" for the coming winter months.
